➜本田这车竟长得和五菱一样，推手动挡飞度替代品，配6速手动变速箱
http://www.sohu.com/a/437703588_99994080	52532
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201211/5e14b0fdfa694174a0a094b6bc3d3ec8.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201211/002f2225d35f4c8692ba26fa83de0ba3.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>本文编辑：</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201211/17ab8d426a1e4784a29173118a61864a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
